'''Delia''' is [[Sandy|Sandy's]] fiancée, who Sandy mentioned during his appearance in [[The One With The Male Nanny]]. Ross asked Sandy if he (Sandy) was gay, causing Rachel to turn in fury, furiously shout-whispering "Ross!!" and Sandy then saying that it was okay because he got that a lot doing what he did, but he corrected Ross by saying that he's straight and engaged and that his fiancée's name is Delia.
